data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis—a 2/1 main home and a 1/1 cottage, each with private entrances and cozy backyards. Ideal for living, investing, or house-hacking, this property offers unmatched flexibility. An inviting atmosphere inside the main house and the back yard has so much to offer.    The curb appeal is a showstopper, and the location is unbeatable. You're minutes from the beach, airport, highway, and a top hospital. Plus, save on energy with installed solar panels. Whether you're seeking a forever home or a prime investment, this is a slice of paradise you'll be proud to own. Schedule your tour today!"
